DOC.brief_summary: This study is being conducted to examine the effect of AZD6140 on the levels of certain chemicals in subjects' blood and urine.
DOC.brief_title: Uric Acid Study in Healthy Male Volunteers
DOC.criteria: Normal physical examination, vital signs, electrocardiogram (ECG) and laboratory values (unless the investigator considers an abnormality not to be clinically significant) Normal laboratory tests at screening Nonsmoker (no cigarette/tobacco use for at least 6 months) Personal or family history of gout, gouty arthritis, or renal stones
